---
description: Gates de qualidade e seguranca para criacao e submissao de plugins Cursor.
globs:
  - "**/.cursor-plugin/plugin.json"
  - "**/.cursor-plugin/marketplace.json"
  - "**/skills/**/SKILL.md"
  - "**/agents/*.md"
  - "**/rules/*.mdc"
  - "**/commands/*.{md,txt}"
alwaysApply: false
